CatDescriptText: St. Benedict the Moor church is located in the former Holy Trinity Church building at 91 Crawford Street.  The parish is a merger with St. Brigid, Holy Trinity, St. Richard, and St. Benedict the Moor.  The Frederick Shrady statue of St. Benedict on top of the bell tower was dedicated in 1968.
TitMainTitle: Crane installing statue of St. Benedict the Moor on top of church bell tower, and Custom Cola billboard in foreground
